Privacy Policy for Aedile Discord Bot
Last Updated: November 21, 2024
1. Introduction
This Privacy Policy explains how Aedile ("we," "us," or "our") collects, uses, and protects information obtained from users ("you" or "users") of our Discord bot. We are committed to protecting your privacy and handling any personal information we obtain with care and respect.
2. Information We Collect
2.1 Automatically Collected Information

Server ID
Channel IDs

2.2 User-Provided Information

Any information you deliberately provide through bot commands (anonymised, runs through console but is not stored)
Custom settings and preferences
Server configuration settings

3. How We Use Information
We use the collected information for:

Providing and maintaining bot functionality
Improving bot features and user experience
Responding to user requests and support inquiries
Preventing abuse and maintaining security
Complying with Discord's Terms of Service

4. Data Storage and Security

4.1 Storage
We do not store any user information or command history

4.2 Security

Access to data is strictly limited to authorized personnel


5. Data Sharing and Disclosure
We do not sell, trade, or rent user information to third parties. We may share data:

When required by law
To protect our rights or property
To prevent abuse or harmful activities
With service providers who assist in our operations (under strict confidentiality agreements)


7. Data Retention
We retain data for:

Active users: As long as necessary to provide services
Inactive users: Up to 180 days after last interaction
Server settings: Until bot removal or explicit deletion request

8. Children's Privacy
The bot is not intended for use by individuals under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect information from children under 13.
9. International Data Transfers
Data may be processed and stored in various locations globally. By using the bot, you consent to the transfer of information to countries outside your country of residence.
10. Changes to Privacy Policy
We reserve the right to update this Privacy Policy at any time. Users will be notified of any material changes through our Discord support server or bot announcements.
11. Cookie Policy
The bot does not use cookies directly, but third-party services we use might employ cookies or similar tracking technologies.
12. Contact Information
For any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us through:

Our Discord support server

